Genome Name: Blautia producta ATCC 27340 = DSM 2950 strain JCM 1471
Sequencing Center: National Institute of Advanced Industrial Science and Technology, Biomedical Research Institute
Comments: This project provides a high quality genome sequence of Blautia producta strain JCM 1471(T).

Sequencing Center: Helmholtz Centre for Environmental Research - UFZ
Comments: Complete sequencing and de novo genome assembly (based on a hybrid strategy of combining PacBio with Illumina) for proteogenomic studies. While RefSeq sequences are available for the strain re-sequencing and assembly using a hybrid strategy ensured one complete genome sequence without any gaps and devoid of any unresolved repeats. These genomes are the basis for further functional studies with particular focus on the identification of short proteins.
